│ emitting a shuffle before its operand definitions dominate it.\n\n5.          │
│ Conclusion:\nBy deferring the combination with Root until after all           │
│ insertelement emissions, we guarantee SSA dominance: definitions of vectors   │
│ via insertelement dominate any shufflevector that uses them. This addresses   │
